org.codemonkey.swiftsocketserver
Class ServerEndpointTCP

java.lang.Object
  org.codemonkey.swiftsocketserver.ServerEndpoint
      org.codemonkey.swiftsocketserver.ServerEndpointTCP

 class ServerEndpointTCP
extends ServerEndpoint

Wrapper that delegates all calls directly to the decorated ServerSocket. The Server Endpoint abstraction mimics how TCP deals with clients and so the TCP server endpoint variant adds no extra functionality, except that it returns client endpoints instead of Socket instances (see getClientEndpoint().

Since:
1.0
Author:
Benny Bottema
